snippet.title: Introducing the Splatoon 3: Expansion Pass! (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
Introducing the Splatoon 3: Expansion Pass! Make Inkopolis your stomping ground when Wave 1 launches this spring, then look forward to a new story when Wave 2's Side Order launches in the future.
